            "title": "Galaxy Digital Non-GAAP EPS of -$0.49 beats by $0.44, revenue of $10.04B beats by $1.29B",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Galaxy Digital <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489801-galaxy-announces-first-quarter-2026-financial-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLXY\" title=\"Galaxy Digital Inc.\">GLXY</a></span>): Q1 Non-GAAP EPS of -$0.49 <span> beats by $0.44</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $10.04B (-22.7% Y/Y) <span> beats by $1.29B</span>.</li>\n<li>Q1 2026 net loss of $(216) million and diluted and adjusted EPS of $(0.49), driven primarily by the depreciation of digital asset prices in the quarter.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
